    "It is apparent that previous papers emphasize the importance but difficulty of rigorously evaluating MT quality and analyzing translation errors.",
    "Neural MT shows promise but still produces critical errors that require human evaluation.",
    "Overall, combining automated metrics and human judgment, particularly for critical semantic errors, provides the most comprehensive MT assessment.",
